## المرحلة 1 — `AuthController.cs` 🔴

### المشكلة
يستخدم `LoginRequest`/`RegisterRequest` من `Models.Requests` و`Models.Responses` (محذوفان)، ويستدعي `RegisterAsync(user, password, roleId)` بشكل مختلف كلياً عن الـ Service الجديد.

### التغييرات

#### [MODIFY] [AuthController.cs](file:///c:/Users/Masoud/source/repos/BloodConnectAPI/BloodConnectAPI/Controllers/AuthController.cs)

**Usings:**
```diff
- using BloodConnectAPI.Models.Requests;
- using BloodConnectAPI.Models.Responses;
+ using BloodConnectAPI.Models.DTOs;
+ using System.Security.Claims;
  using BloodConnectAPI.Service.Common;
  using BloodConnectAPI.Service.Interfaces;
  using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization;
  using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Mvc;
```

**`POST /auth/login`:**
```diff
- [ProducesResponseType(typeof(ServiceResponse<LoginResponse>), 200)]
+ [ProducesResponseType(typeof(ServiceResponse<LoginResponseDto>), 200)]
- public async Task<IActionResult> Login([FromBody] LoginRequest request)
+ public async Task<IActionResult> Login([FromBody] LoginDto request)
- var response = await _authService.LoginAsync(request.Username, request.Password);
+ var response = await _authService.LoginAsync(request);
```

**`POST /auth/register`:**
```diff
- [ProducesResponseType(typeof(ServiceResponse<BloodConnectAPI.Models.User>), 201)]
+ [ProducesResponseType(typeof(ServiceResponse<ApplicationUserDto>), 201)]
- public async Task<IActionResult> Register([FromBody] RegisterRequest request)
+ public async Task<IActionResult> Register([FromBody] RegisterDto request)

- // حذف إنشاء User يدوياً كلياً
- var user = new BloodConnectAPI.Models.User { ... };
- var response = await _authService.RegisterAsync(user, request.Password, request.RoleId);
+ var response = await _authService.RegisterAsync(request);
```

**`POST /auth/change-password`:**
```diff
// تغيير نوع UserId من int إلى string
// إضافة [Authorize] لاستخراج UserId من JWT
+ [Authorize]
  public async Task<IActionResult> ChangePassword([FromBody] ChangePasswordRequest request)
+ // استخراج userId من Claims بدلاً من قبوله في الـ body
+ var userId = User.FindFirstValue(ClaimTypes.NameIdentifier)!;
  var response = await _authService.ChangePasswordAsync(userId, request.CurrentPassword, request.NewPassword);
```

> [!NOTE]
> يجب إنشاء `ChangePasswordRequest` بسيط يحتوي فقط على `CurrentPassword` و`NewPassword` (بدون `UserId` في الـ body).

