## المرحلة 3 — `DonorsController.cs` 🟡

### المشكلة
`userId` كـ `int` بدل `string` في `LinkDonorToUser`، ومفقودة 3 Endpoints للميزات الجديدة.

### التغييرات

#### [MODIFY] [DonorsController.cs](file:///c:/Users/Masoud/source/repos/BloodConnectAPI/BloodConnectAPI/Controllers/DonorsController.cs)

**Usings:**
```diff
+ using BloodConnectAPI.Models.Enums;
+ using Microsoft.AspNetCore.Authorization;
+ using System.Security.Claims;
```

**`POST /donors/{donorId}/link-user/{userId}` — إصلاح نوع البيانات:**
```diff
- public async Task<IActionResult> LinkDonorToUser(int donorId, int userId)
+ [Authorize(Roles = "Admin")]
+ public async Task<IActionResult> LinkDonorToUser(int donorId, string userId)
```

**إضافة `POST /donors/{id}/approve` — [NEW]:**
```csharp
[HttpPost("{id}/approve")]
[Authorize(Roles = "Admin")]
[ProducesResponseType(typeof(ServiceResponse<DonorDto>), 200)]
public async Task<IActionResult> ApproveDonor(int id, [FromBody] ApproveDonorDto dto)
{
    var reviewerId = User.FindFirstValue(ClaimTypes.NameIdentifier)!;
    var response = await _donorService.ApproveDonorAsync(id, dto, reviewerId);
    if (!response.Success) return BadRequest(response);
    return Ok(response);
}
```

**إضافة `GET /donors/by-status/{status}` — [NEW]:**
```csharp
[HttpGet("by-status/{status}")]
[Authorize(Roles = "Admin")]
[ProducesResponseType(typeof(ServiceResponse<PagedResult<DonorDto>>), 200)]
public async Task<IActionResult> GetByApprovalStatus(
    DonorApprovalStatus status, [FromQuery] PaginationParams pagination)
{
    var response = await _donorService.GetByApprovalStatusAsync(status, pagination);
    return Ok(response);
}
```

**إضافة `GET /donors/{id}/medical-documents` — [NEW]:**
```csharp
[HttpGet("{id}/medical-documents")]
[Authorize(Roles = "Admin")]
[ProducesResponseType(typeof(ServiceResponse<IEnumerable<DonorMedicalDocumentDto>>), 200)]
public async Task<IActionResult> GetMedicalDocuments(int id)
{
    var response = await _donorService.GetMedicalDocumentsAsync(id);
    if (!response.Success) return NotFound(response);
    return Ok(response);
}
```

> [!NOTE]
> نضيف `[Authorize]` على مستوى الـ Controller لحماية جميع العمليات مع استثناء GET للعامة إن لزم.

